<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246221>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Rambla’s organ in Miopsalis and Meghalaya: A, Miopsalis gryllospeca (Shear 1993) type; B, undescribed species of Miopsalis from Borneo (“ Borneo sp. 18 ”, MCZ DNA 103262); C – D, undescribed species of Miopsalis from Borneo (“ Borneo sp. 13 ”, MCZ DNA 101517); E – F, undescribed species of Meghalaya from the Thai-Malay Peninsula (“ Peninsula sp. 19 d ”, MCZ DNA 101094, 101500)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246221/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

